eval("__webpack_require__.r(__webpack_exports__);\n/* harmony default export */ __webpack_exports__[\"default\"] = (\"---\\ntype: page\\ntitle: About\\ndate: 2020-01-01\\n---\\n\\n# Shu Ding\\n\\nShu (b. 1994, China) is a designer and developer focusing on visual ideas.\\n\\nStarted programming in high school and has since spent 4 years on **algorithm competitions**, Shu worked as a **graphic designer and web developer** in Shanghai, and got his BSc degree in **Computer Science** from Fudan University. He also enjoys creating **game and HCI prototypes** as side projects.\\n\\nShu always sees “Be curious. Read widely. Try new things.” (by [Aaron Swartz](http://aaronsw.com/)) as the guide to [creativity](https://spectrum.mit.edu/winter-2017/neri-oxmans-krebs-cycle-of-creativity).\\n\\nGet in touch via [Twitter](https://twitter.com/shuding_) DM or email g@shud.in.\\n\\n---\\n\\n<details><summary children=\\\"CV\\\"/>\\n\\n### Experience\\n\\n- Web development and design at [Vercel](https://vercel.com/about) (formerly ZEIT), 2018–present\\n- Software engineer at Microsoft, 2017–2018\\n- Bachelor of Computer Science at Fudan University. Shanghai, China, 2013–2017\\n\\n### Web Design & Development\\n\\n- [Vercel](https://vercel.com) dashboard development\\n- [SWR](https://github.com/vercel/swr) creator and maintainer\\n- [nextjs.org](https://next-site-ivyycdnshp.now.sh/) design & development ([src](https://github.com/zeit/next-site))\\n- [VRS](https://v-r-s.now.sh/edit/?id=1) design & development ([src](https://github.com/zeit/vrs))\\n- [inns.studio](https://inns.studio/)\\n- [HACK×FDU](http://fdu2016.hackx.org/)\\n- [more...](https://github.com/shuding)\\n\\n### HCI & Game Design\\n\\n- [Out of Bounds Exception](https://twitter.com/cyatheatree/status/988836359518351360), a puzzle game prototype. 2018\\n- [The Spectator](http://cyatheatree.com/projects/the-spectator.html). 2017\\n- [Mak](https://inns.studio/mak), an experiment on text editors and note taking. 2017\\n- [Flappy Cube](https://github.com/shuding/flappy-cube), a demo of exploration on visual effects in 2D platformer games. 2017\\n- [Pouring Ball](http://cyatheatree.com/projects/pouring-ball.html). 2015\\n- [y86.js.org](https://y86.js.org/), Y86 CPU Visualization. 2015\\n- [Animator](https://github.com/shuding/animator), a Flash-like tool to create simple animations. 2014\\n\\n### Awards & Honors\\n\\n- [Game grant winner](http://the-witness.net/news/2018/06/congratulations-to-the-grant-recipients/) from Thekla (makers of *The Witness* and *Braid*), 2018\\n- Top 30. Tencent GAD Game Innovation Competition 2016\\n- Outstanding Creative Awards (10 teams), Tencent TPai Student Innovation & Entrepreneurship Competition 2016\\n- 1st place. [HackShanghai 2015](http://2015.hackshanghai.com/), China’s largest hackathon\\n- 6th place. [MegCup 2015](https://2015.megcup.com/)\\n- Gold Medal, 8th place. [ACM-ICPC Asia Regional Contest 2013](https://icpc.baylor.edu/regionals/finder/chengdu-2013/standings)\\n- First prize (&lt;1% nationwide, 2nd place in Hubei provience). NOIP (China National Olympiad in Informatics in Provinces) 2012\\n- Bronze Medal. NOI (China National Olympiad in Informatics) 2012\\n- First prize. NOIP 2011\\n- Bronze Medal. NOI 2011\\n\\n### Features\\n\\n- [China app gives shy students a virtual voice — Reuters](https://www.reuters.com/video/2015/12/04/china-app-gives-shy-students-a-virtual-v?videoId=366561295)\\n- [A Win For \\\"Pouring Ball\\\" — China Plus](http://english.cri.cn/7146/2015/12/01/3481s906479.htm)\\n- Empowering Frontend Apps with Serverless Next.js — Alibaba D2\\n\\n### Links\\n\\n- [Photography](https://works.shud.in)\\n- [Books](https://book.douban.com/people/ParabolaWorld/collect?start=0&sort=time&rating=all&filter=all&mode=list) / [Movies](https://movie.douban.com/people/ParabolaWorld/collect?sort=time&start=0&filter=all&mode=list&tags_sort=count)\\n- [Clippings](https://getpocket.com/@parabola_ds) from my reading list\\n- [Pinboard](https://pinboard.in/u:parabola) web links\\n- [Cargo](https://cargocollective.com/quietshu), graphic design archives, 2013-2016\\n- [GitHub](https://github.com/shuding), [Twitter](https://twitter.com/shuding_)\\n- [Wikipedia](https://zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%B4%A1%E7%8C%AE&offset=&limit=500&contribs=user&target=Iamds&namespace=2&nsInvert=1&tagfilter=&start=&end=), [MDN](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/profiles/shuding), [Stack Overflow](https://stackoverflow.com/users/2424786/shu-ding), [Instagram](https://instagram.com/_shuding), [Flickr](https://www.flickr.com/photos/shuding/)\\n\\n</details>\");//# sourceURL=[module]\n//# sourceMappingURL=data:application/json;charset=utf-8;base64,\n//# sourceURL=webpack-internal:///./pages/index.md\n");

